title: Emergency warning issued as out-of-control bushfire rages across Sydney
text:
Emergency warning issued as out-of-control bushfire rages across Sydney 10:57am EDT - 00:56 
An emergency warning was reissued on Sunday for an out-of-control bushfire that is raging across parts of the Australian city of Sydney. Ed Giles reports.
